### Health Check
GET {{BusReservationSystem.WebApi_HostAddress}}/api/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Search Available Buses - Valid Request
GET {{BusReservationSystem.WebApi_HostAddress}}/api/search?from=Dhaka&to=Chittagong&journeyDate=2025-10-30
Accept: application/json

###

### Search Available Buses - Another Route
